'''休閒宮'''（{{lang-de|Kurhaus}}）<ref name="Metzelthin1983">{{cite book|last=Metzelthin|first=Pearl Violette Newfield|title=Gourmet|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=26ryAAAAMAAJ|accessdate=3 April 2012|year=1983|publisher=Condé Nast Publications|page=24}}</ref>是位於[[德國|德國]][[黑森州|黑森州]]首府[[威斯巴登|威斯巴登]]的一座[[溫泉|溫泉]]建築。現在是威斯巴登的會議中心<ref name="Schulte-Peevers2010">{{cite book|last=Schulte-Peevers|first=Andrea|title=Germany|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=IyM0vxYFaFUC&pg=PA547|accessdate=3 April 2012|date=1 March 2010|publisher=Lonely Planet|isbn=978-1-74104-781-3|pages=547–}}</ref>，也是許多大型活動的舉辦地。休閒宮除了會議廳和餐廳之外，還有賭場設施<ref name="Bekker2005">{{cite book|last=Bekker|first=Henk|title=Adventure Guide Germany|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=28XjYLVEpUoC&pg=PA321|accessdate=3 April 2012|date=15 September 2005|publisher=Hunter Publishing, Inc|isbn=978-1-58843-503-3|pages=321–|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213090242/https://books.google.com/books?id=28XjYLVEpUoC&pg=PA321&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Coupe2009">{{cite book|last=Coupe|first=Alison|title=Michelin Travel Guide Germany|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=nO-gzYtSaGoC&pg=PA540|accessdate=3 April 2012|date=15 May 2009|publisher=Michelin|isbn=978-1-906261-38-2|pages=540–}}</ref>。

